msgctxt "108_Trendy Senpai"
msgid "It's an app for your PC or cell phone that lets you play stuff like pachinko or slots."
msgstr "It's an app for your PC or cell phone that lets you play stuff like pachinko or slots."

msgctxt "120_Trendy Senpai"
msgid "I got my girlfriend into it, and now she can't stop playing!"
msgstr "I got my girlfriend into it, and now she can't stop playing!"

msgctxt "132_Early Bird Friend"
msgid "Really? You sure are good with women. You always know the right thing to say to them!"
msgstr "Really? You sure are good with women. You always know the right thing to say to them!"

msgctxt "144_Trendy Senpai"
msgid "Comes with the territory, man."
msgstr "Comes with the territory, man."

msgctxt "156_Trendy Senpai"
msgid "Problem is, she's been spending so much time on 777 Town, she barely has any time to hang out with me... I'm telling ya, it's a curse, not a gift."
msgstr "Problem is, she's been spending so much time on 777 Town, she barely has any time to hang out with me... I'm telling ya, it's a curse, not a gift."

